# Krishi Bondho API Documentation 🚀

This document provides a detailed list of all available API endpoints for the Krishi Bondho (কৃষি বন্ধু) backend, including required request bodies and parameters.

**Base URL**: `http://localhost:8000/api/v1`

---

## 🔐 Authentication Modules
`Base Path: /api/v1/auth`

| Method | Endpoint | Body Data (JSON) | Params | Auth |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/register` | `{ name, email, password }` | - | No |
| `POST` | `/verify` | `{ email, otp }` | - | No |
| `POST` | `/login` | `{ email, password }` | - | No |
| `POST` | `/resend-otp` | `{ email }` | - | No |
| `PATCH` | `/change-password`| `{ oldPassword, newPassword }` | - | Yes |
| `POST` | `/logout` | - | - | Yes |
| `GET` | `/me` | - | - | Yes |
| `PATCH` | `/toggle-two-factor`| - | - | Yes |

---

## 👤 User Management
`Base Path: /api/v1/users`

| Method | Endpoint | Body Data | Params | Auth |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET` | `/` | - | `page`, `limit` | Yes (Admin) |
| `PATCH` | `/me/avatar` | `FormData { avatar: file }` | - | Yes |
| `PATCH` | `/me/profile` | `{ name }` | - | Yes |
| `PATCH` | `/notification` | `{ type, value }` | - | Yes |

> **Note on `/notification`**: `type` can be `email`, `system_notification`, or `safety_alert`. `value` is boolean.

---

## 🤖 AI Agricultural Chat
`Base Path: /api/v1/chat`

| Method | Endpoint | Body Data (JSON) | Params | Auth |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/` | `{ message, userId, chatId? }` | - | Yes |
| `POST` | `/stream` | `{ message, userId, chatId? }` | - | Yes |
| `GET` | `/all` | - | - | Yes |
| `GET` | `/:chatId` | - | `chatId` | Yes |
| `DELETE` | `/:chatId` | - | `chatId` | Yes |

---

## 🌾 Crop Advisor
`Base Path: /api/v1/crop`

| Method | Endpoint | Body Data (JSON) | Params | Auth |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/` | `{ location, season, soil, userId }` | - | Yes |

